    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stack Machines</strong> is an open-ended puzzle programming game. Use the stack data structure in the form of 4 stack machines moving according to the modules(instructions) placed on a grid to read, transform and output different input sequences. Optimize your solutions for size, module count, speed and cost-effectiveness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 stacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wrapping resizable board</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-ended puzzles with a lot of potential for optimization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 optimization metrics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recording of solution videos </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Histograms</p></li></ul>",
